  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269604</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_040_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>これは……
デリス・カーラーンの……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That is...Derris Kharlan's...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269688</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_040_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あの戦争での
ダオスの記憶……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>He was pondering over the facts of the war...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269752</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_040_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ダオス……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Dhaos...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269872</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_040_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そして、パレスグドラは……
……わたしたちは、
魔科学兵器を使ったんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And then...his suspicions became
reality... When Palace Gudora–we
used the Mana Cannon...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269976</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_040_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ダオスも苦しんでた。
ただ、戦争を
見てただけじゃない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Dhaos was suffering too. But,
he was just analyzing the war.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270184</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_040_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>違うよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270184</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_040_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ただ見てただけなんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>He had to stay calm and analyze
the war for his people.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270184</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_040_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だからこそ、
彼は苦しんだんだよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Not being able to think of other
actions ate away at him...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270184</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_040_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>見てただけの罪を
彼は背負い続けてきた……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>He was burdened with the sin
of just observing and forever
cursed himself for his inaction...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>3</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
